{"tid":2497862,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"4台聯播觀後感","createTime":"2021-04-20T20:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T21:37:13.000Z","uid":17360,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e7e1f23820889d3a59f6e63e9e65049d3a4def","tid":2497862,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:28:01.000Z","msg":"首先最可惜無睇到熊仔頭條live<br />\n<br />\n無辦法講得太全面啦<br />\n<br />\n拿其實呢 啱啱嘗試合作<br />\n<br />\n有錯呢，咪改囉<br />\n<br />\n跌低咪起返身囉 <br />\n<br />\n做錯可以屌既 但要比機會人囉<br />\n<br />\n都唔明點解咁多人都咁暴躁<br />\n<br />\n成個小朋友咁 唔識控制情緒 <br />\n<br />\n一興奮就屌 過度活躍症兼反社會人格<br />\n<br />\n咁4班人平時又唔係話特別friend<br />\n<br />\n仲要大家唔同圈子 style又唔同<br />\n<br />\n體諒下啦 咁難得真係有&quot;咁大件事&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外辛苦曬豪哥哥，咁勤力帶風向<br />\n<br />\n越亂越好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有成件事完咗之後<br />\n<br />\n4台全世界都救緊件事<br />\n<br />\n都係個句 體諒下啦<br />\n<br />\n我就收貨既 希望你地下次做得更好<br />\n<br />\n試當真啊嘛 咪試下先囉"},{"pid":"d60282df60fee80e5f08ef249ed9efed2915b6e8","tid":2497862,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:28:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c93ee61ed5fabfbbdd7102d4eca5dbf37f7af9f6","tid":2497862,"uid":17360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:28:54.000Z","msg":"連登正能量"},{"pid":"09fcbdb6b729feb291cd3332fdfbef83398452cd","tid":2497862,"uid":17360,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:30:30.000Z","msg":"希望下次有埋好青年荼毒室<br />\n<br />\n想睇豬文爆seed <br />\n<br />\n4哥片全世界<br />\n<br />\n白水氣氛擔當 一笑解千仇"},{"pid":"a226b25084b1b74ae91a0e6119333558a72b5721","tid":2497862,"uid":199925,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T20:32:29.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我好唔中意睇試當真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD聲又時大時細<br />\nD鏡頭又飛黎飛去<br />\n另外三個channel睇都冇呢個問題"},{"pid":"d330f22a555cd703ce8173d71e61ff89ca1f5dd6","tid":2497862,"uid":17360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a226b25084b1